originalText.text: I love the lip balm!  Definitely recommend it to everyone. It feels completely natural on the lips, and there is a very faint scent of ( I think it is ) coconut oil. The balm is moisturizing but not too greasy.  I especially like the faint red taint which comes from alkanet root. It gives your lips a color as if you just ate some raspberries.  Very natural, very beautiful lip color.

originalText.text:
I have tried a few products from Soulfulbodyinc and love them all. I like the fact that they are all natural and organic. The ingredients and instructions are listed on the products.
The lip balm is one product that everyone is talking about. It is so smooth and luscious. It gives your lips the right amount of color.
The other product I love is the face wash. It smells great and make my face feel so soft. And, when you want to take off the dead skin, nothing is better than the Green Detox face mask. It leaves my skin clean and smooth.
If you want to balance the "doshas" in your body, take the quiz on website to determine your constitution (dosha). Get the tea or the box according to your dosha and balance you body and mind.
I love the fact that this company takes care of my body and my soul. Has such a fitting name (soulfulbody). Try them, you won't regret!
